			<div class="similar_data">
			     <ul>
                 	<li>
                    	<div class="s_img"><a href="#"><img src="/img/cart_01.jpg" /></div>
                        <div class="s_info">
                        	<p>SAP销售与分销实施指南</p>
                            <b>￥59.30</b>
